## Limitations

The analysis is based on secondary sources, which may contain biases or incomplete information. The lack of primary sources limits the depth of understanding regarding the personal motivations and internal political dynamics of the dictatorships. Additionally, the complexity of international relations and the multitude of factors leading to World War II mean that this report can only provide a high-level overview rather than an exhaustive analysis.